  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >18世纪的欧洲，教会的一名见习修女，被指派了一个不属于新人的任务。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不以真面目示人的神秘雇主，被诅咒的恶灵徘徊的庄园， </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >等待着她的……将会是怎样的命运？ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >——“普通的驱魔仪式无效的话，就请用其他方式尽快开始您的工作吧？”</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >+ 奇幻中世纪背景下的乙女向多路线视觉小说。</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > + 角色介绍 + </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209620/extras/172546db3e7076ab04f73cbe4be1f98e.avif?t=1743485877\" width=328 height=377 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主啊，我请求您，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >求您降临，带着您的威严降临于此，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >求您降临，解救那些仍在彷徨的灵魂。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209620/extras/d197c1a1f3dccea14e1734798c7c30f5.avif?t=1743485877\" width=328 height=380 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果是由可爱的修女小姐来提问的话，我可是会好好回答的，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不过就算如此……恐怕那些答案还是会让你失望哦？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209620/extras/bb93e7d4cbb450df705ebc5622c2e127.avif?t=1743485877\" width=328 height=380 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >告知我你的名字，后续我会以待客之道对待你……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >即便是以现在的这幅状态。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209620/extras/c225473c17cdacfe15f93ca1f41197b0.avif?t=1743485877\" width=328 height=377 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 如果在这里获得的第一份记忆是与你有关的，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >虽说我已经没得选择，但是就结果而言也不算太坏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209620/extras/fe51141c70b83f10e0837f3bef738e27.avif?t=1743485877\" width=328 height=377 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >那么，你就是负责这次工作的修女？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >告诉我你的答案吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209620/extras/ea98ee97ec34437de7346e3cb3458722.avif?t=1743485877\" width=328 height=377 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有事？</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >+ 游戏系统 + </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >+ 通过前往不同地点行动收集情报，解锁角色们过去的故事，并一起迎接新的未来吧。</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209620/extras/1949203866cf3501b59c0dde007ac17f.avif?t=1743485877\" width=800 height=1325 /></span><br>+ 游戏特色 + </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >+ 35万以上文本，数十张CG，3位主要可攻略角色+全员均有专属结局。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209620/extras/dee7c4be9dd292f4708f8096bf64687a.avif?t=1743485877\" width=800 height=889 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >总之，无论是白天的情报收集，还是夜晚的活跃，一切都为了下一次的——重逢。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*感谢来自ACON3D的Urry，Geobugwang，martini，1yr 12m atelier，TteokbokkiJMT，Migwang，Yan，EL_Tau，Preppy，Sempreblue所提供的背景模型素材。</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >18世纪的欧洲，教会的一名见习修女，被指派了一个不属于新人的任务。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不以真面目示人的神秘雇主，被诅咒的恶灵徘徊的庄园， </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >等待着她的……将会是怎样的命运？ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >——“普通的驱魔仪式无效的话，就请用其他方式尽快开始您的工作吧？”</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >+ 奇幻中世纪背景下的乙女向多路线视觉小说。</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > + 角色介绍 + </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209620/extras/172546db3e7076ab04f73cbe4be1f98e.avif?t=1743485877\" width=328 height=377 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主啊，我请求您，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >求您降临，带着您的威严降临于此，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >求您降临，解救那些仍在彷徨的灵魂。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209620/extras/d197c1a1f3dccea14e1734798c7c30f5.avif?t=1743485877\" width=328 height=380 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果是由可爱的修女小姐来提问的话，我可是会好好回答的，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不过就算如此……恐怕那些答案还是会让你失望哦？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209620/extras/bb93e7d4cbb450df705ebc5622c2e127.avif?t=1743485877\" width=328 height=380 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >告知我你的名字，后续我会以待客之道对待你……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >即便是以现在的这幅状态。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209620/extras/c225473c17cdacfe15f93ca1f41197b0.avif?t=1743485877\" width=328 height=377 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 如果在这里获得的第一份记忆是与你有关的，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >虽说我已经没得选择，但是就结果而言也不算太坏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/a